    {
      "text": "To initiate upon positive pregnancy test. Monthly anti-Xa level monitoring (target peak 0.2-0.6 IU/mL). Dose adjustment if significant weight change. Transition to unfractionated heparin at 36 weeks. Hold 24h before planned delivery. Resume 6-12h postpartum (vaginal) or 12-24h (cesarean). Continue or transition to warfarin for 6 weeks postpartum."
